---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import LandingHeader from '../../components/LandingHeader.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About Us | AI Agent Platform | VivaSpeak"
  description="VivaSpeak: conversational AI agent platform. Voice, web chat, WhatsApp, CRM and Salesforce integration. Multi-location and editable knowledge base."
  canonical="https://vivaspeak.com/en/about/"
  alternateEs="https://vivaspeak.com/sobre-nosotros/"
  alternateEn="https://vivaspeak.com/en/about/"
  lang="en"
  schemaAboutPage={true}
  speakable={['.about-content > p:first-of-type', '.about-content h2', '.about-content h2 + p']}
>
  <LandingHeader lang="en" ctaLabel="Request demo" ctaHref="/en/#schedule" secondaryHref="/en/" />

  <main id="main-content">
    <section class="section about-page">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="about-content">
          <h1>About VivaSpeak</h1>

          <p>
            VivaSpeak develops conversational AI agents for businesses that need to automate calls,
            web chat and digital channels 24/7. Our platform lets you configure agent behavior,
            prompts and knowledge base, integrating with CRMs like Salesforce, calendars and
            internal systems.
          </p>

          <p>
            We're not just a voice agent. VivaSpeak is a platform where each company defines how
            their assistant should behave: what information it can provide, how it should close
            appointments and what data to record. Everything is centralized in a panel with
            transcripts, metrics and automations.
          </p>

          <h2>Who we are</h2>
          <p>
            We work with clinics, real estate agencies and service companies in Spain and Latin
            America. We are a team specialized in customer service automation and development of
            conversational AI agents for businesses that handle high call volumes.
          </p>

          <h2>Platform</h2>
          <p>From the VivaSpeak panel you can:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Edit the agent's knowledge base.</li>
            <li>Configure routing rules by location or promotion.</li>
            <li>Integrate Salesforce or other CRMs via API.</li>
            <li>Manage leads in a built-in lightweight CRM.</li>
            <li>Enable voice agent, web chat or both on the same knowledge.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main></Layout
>

<h2>Sectors</h2>
<ul>
  <li>
    <strong>Clinics</strong> — Virtual assistant for clinics: schedules appointments, checks availability
    and manages reception 24/7.
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Real estate</strong> — Multi-location intelligent switchboard, lead capture, automatic filtering
    by promotion and direct CRM registration.
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>HR</strong> — Call automation for recruitment: screens candidates and schedules interviews.
  </li>
</ul>

<h2>Integrations</h2>
<p>
  Integration with WhatsApp Business API, Google Calendar, Microsoft Bookings, Salesforce and other
  CRMs via API. Compatible with WordPress and corporate sites to install web chat in minutes.
</p>

<h2>Contact</h2>
<p>
  To learn more about how an AI voice agent can help you,
  <a href="/en/#schedule">schedule a free demo</a> or email us at
  <a href="mailto:hello@vivaspeak.com">hello@vivaspeak.com</a>. You can also call
  <a href="tel:+34951798932">+34 951 798 932</a> — Valeria, our AI voice agent, will answer.
</p>
<p class="about-cta">
  <a href="/en/" class="btn btn-primary">Back to home</a>
</p>

<h2>Intelligent Automation for Businesses</h2>
<p>
  VivaSpeak combines voice agent, web chatbot and CRM integration in a single platform. Automates
  inbound calls, logs opportunities in Salesforce, sends promotion information and enables
  multi-location support scaling without expanding human teams.
</p>

<Footer lang="en" />

<style>
  .about-page {
    padding-top: calc(var(--space-20) + var(--space-4));
  }

  .about-content {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-content h1 {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: var(--font-extrabold);
    color: var(--primary-dark);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-8);
    text-align: center;
    line-height: var(--leading-tight);
  }

  .about-content h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: var(--font-bold);
    color: var(--gray-900);
    margin: var(--space-10) 0 var(--space-3);
    line-height: var(--leading-tight);
  }

  .about-content p {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-4);
  }

  .about-content ul {
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-4) var(--space-5);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .about-content li {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .about-content a {
    color: var(--primary-dark);
    font-weight: var(--font-semibold);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .about-content a:hover {
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .about-cta {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: var(--space-8);
  }
</style>
